data.description: This is one you won’t want to miss! This gorgeous two story move in ready home has 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths. With both a family room and living room with a beautiful fireplace. Perfect for a family! Main floor laundry for extra convenience. Beautiful wood floors throughout. Furnace was installed in 2022, A/C was installed in 2021. Most windows were installed in 2012 and 2015. So much of the big stuff is already done for you. The backyard has a great deck with a gazebo and hot tub that will both stay for the new owners! But the best part is that this home has no neighbors on one side. That side is the IHM Sisters sprawling open area. Watch for deer, fox and other wildlife as well as catching some gorgeous sunsets. Schedule your showing asap! This home is well loved and many will find it just perfect.
